OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FClimate change: New schools
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin Wales must be net zero  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffrom 2022                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, New school and college buildings in    
OL,6, Wales will have to meet net zero       
OL,7, targets from January.                  
OL,9,FMajor refurbishments, extensions and   
OL,10,Fnew builds will have to be in line with
OL,11,Fstandards aimed at achieving maximum   
OL,12,Fenergy efficiency.                     
OL,14,FLlancarfan Primary School will be the  
OL,15,Ffirst new school.                      
OL,17,FEducation minister Jeremy Miles said   
OL,18,Fthe new rules would help reverse       
OL,19,Fclimate change damage.                 
